A Proxima Centauri
é a estrela mais próxima.

237
00:14:28,823 --> 00:14:34,162
Os corpos celestiais seguintes são
a Alpha Centauri A, Toli,

238
00:14:34,537 --> 00:14:37,456
a Estrela de Barnard, Wolf 359,

239
00:14:43,130 --> 00:14:47,425
Lalande 21185, Sírio A, Sírio B,

240
00:14:47,675 --> 00:14:51,512
BL Ceti, UV Ceti, Ross 154,

241
00:14:53,181 --> 00:14:54,224
Ross 248,

242
00:14:56,894 --> 00:15:02,024
Epsilon Eridani, Lacaille 9352,
Ross 128,

243
00:15:02,565 --> 00:15:05,776
