261
00:16:33,656 --> 00:16:35,242
Com licença, minha senhora.

262
00:16:37,660 --> 00:16:38,828
Sheldon?

263
00:16:39,829 --> 00:16:40,955
Bolas!

264
00:16:42,457 --> 00:16:46,003
